<section xml:id="sec-separabble" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Separable Differential Equations</title>

  <introduction>
<p>
  Separable ODEs are a common family of differential equations, showing up in many applications!
  It turns out they are well understood, so we will learn how to solve them in this section. 
  We also will examine some applications where separable ODEs naturally arise.
</p>
  </introduction>

